senselogic.sitevision.api.script

Interface InstanceTypeUtil


  • @Requireable(value="InstanceTypeUtil")
public interface InstanceTypeUtil
    Instance type utility interface.

    An instance of the Sitevision class implementing this interface can be obtained via Utils.getInstanceTypeUtil(). See Utils for how to obtain an instance of the Utils interface.

    Since:
    Sitevision 2.6.2
